# GLOBAL CANCER ANALYTICS
## Severity • Survival • Economic Burden Modeling (2015–2024)

---

## PROJECT SUMMARY

A full-scale data analytics and machine learning project analyzing 50,000+ global cancer patient records across 10 countries.

This project combines:
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Statistical hypothesis testing
- Interaction modeling
- Machine Learning (Random Forest)
- Economic burden assessment

The objective is to extract clinically and economically meaningful insights from structured healthcare data.

---

